This is Veles Core Raspberry-PI Linux release (arm-linux-gnueabihf).


## About Veles
Veles Core is innovative cryptocurrency supporting multiple 
PoW algorithms, with unique dynamic block reward system. 
Main goal of the project is to implement decentralised VPN solution 
to protect privacy and anonymity of Internet users around the globe.


## Installation
To install, enter directory containing this README file and simply 
run following command:

make install

This will perform standard installation including Veles Core
command-line and graphical interfaces, manual pages 
and desktop icon.

Alternative modes of installation:
make install-cli	Installs daemon and command-line client only
make install-gui	Installs only graphical interface, no daemon


